metadata.name: Underwater people
metadata.description:
- Do you know that intelligent creatures live under water?  
- Is this a fairy tale? 
- No, the whales are real!

These creatures look like underwater people.  They can communicate and live in society. They can talk to each other and even have a second brain for that. What a miracle!
